summary: This script copies and pipes data to Redis, using Python scripts for processing. The name should be finite and may need to register with something else. It retrieves the recent command for execution.

#!/bin/bash

cp /dev/shm/xvfb/Xvfb_screen0 /dev/shm/xvfb/DOS && cat /dev/shm/xvfb/DOS | pypy3  pypy_xwd.py --raw | python3 rup.py
